40 double Get(std::string const & nm) {
41  Local<String> getName = Nan::New<String>(nm).ToLocalChecked();
42 
43  auto rObj = inp->ToObject()->Get(getName);
44  if (rObj->IsUndefined()) {
45  ThrowTypeError(std::string("Get method in phast.h: " + nm + " not present in object").c_str());
46  }
47  return rObj->NumberValue();
48 }

53  Nan::Set(r, getName, getNum);
54 }
